      "description": "Offering a peerless E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The high-revving power plant delivers a linear torque curve up to its 8,400 RPM redline, supported by a perfectly calibrated M-variable differential. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible swirl marks or rock chips, while the interior Novillo leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. The undercarriage is clinically clean, reflecting a climate-controlled life with no oxidative stress on the suspension components or subframe.",
